Third-Party Content
===================

CHAPS contains no third-party code. The scripts use only built-in
Windows facilities (PowerShell cmdlets, CMD commands, registry, WMI,
netsh, wevtutil, auditpol, etc.).

Reference materials cited in docs/REMEDIATION.md and the analyzer
knowledge base (CIS Benchmarks, DISA STIGs, Microsoft documentation)
are referenced for understanding only. CHAPS does not redistribute
their content.
